14:35.074 --> 14:36.974
[GASPING]
Because you're choking me.

14:36.976 --> 14:38.225
[GRUNTS]

14:40.479 --> 14:42.680
MAN [ON TV]:
<i>We now return</i>
<i>to the E! Network's</i>

14:42.682 --> 14:45.516
100 Greatest Celebrity
Nip-Slips,

14:45.518 --> 14:47.785
Cheek-Peeks and Shaft-Gaffes.

14:47.787 --> 14:49.721
Cleveland,
would you mind making me

14:49.723 --> 14:51.789
another little plate
of pickles and carrots

14:51.791 --> 14:53.190
and black olives and stuff?

14:53.192 --> 14:56.293
Hmm, yeah, plate of pickles.
Fix the gutters. Charity dinner.

14:56.295 --> 14:58.629
Is that Billy Crystal
shaft-gaffing?

14:59.832 --> 15:01.499
[KNOCK AT DOOR]

15:07.840 --> 15:10.207
Tim, I thought I told you
and your buddies

15:10.209 --> 15:12.143
to stay the hell
away from my house.

15:12.145 --> 15:14.012
Yeah, yeah, you did, you did.

15:14.014 --> 15:16.748
And, uh, then this morning,
I remembered something.

15:16.750 --> 15:18.566
I, um-- I'm a bear.

15:18.568 --> 15:23.437
I can kill you, maul you,
rip your face off and eat you.

15:23.439 --> 15:25.139
And I won't even go to jail,

15:25.141 --> 15:28.376
you know, 'cause--
Because I'm a bear.

15:28.378 --> 15:30.979
I think, you know,
in the heat of the moment,

15:30.981 --> 15:32.947
I kind of forgot that.

15:32.949 --> 15:35.950
But, uh, yeah, I'm a bear.
I can kill you.

15:35.952 --> 15:39.453
So tell Cleveland the truth,
because if you don't:

15:39.455 --> 15:42.190
[ROARS]

15:42.192 --> 15:43.291
[CHUCKLES]

15:43.293 --> 15:45.960
Okay. Okay, byesies.

15:47.462 --> 15:49.013
Oh, come on.

15:49.015 --> 15:52.383
Junior, why are your socks
in the refrigerator?

15:52.385 --> 15:54.685
JUNIOR:
My feet get hot.

15:54.687 --> 15:57.321
Cleveland, can we talk?

15:57.323 --> 15:58.856
[GASPS]
You can walk.

15:58.858 --> 16:02.527
Oh, hail the alien
overlord Xenu.

16:02.529 --> 16:05.596
No, baby, listen to me.
I tricked you.

16:05.598 --> 16:08.899
I'm sorry.
I didn't really break my legs.

16:08.901 --> 16:12.036
Ruin her credit rating, Xenu.

16:12.038 --> 16:14.972
I realized I do every damn thing
around this house

16:14.974 --> 16:16.941
while you sit on your butt
watching sports.

16:16.943 --> 16:20.211
So I asked Dr. Fist
to make me some fake casts.

16:20.213 --> 16:21.512
And he did.

16:21.514 --> 16:23.197
I think because he wants
to sleep with me.

16:23.199 --> 16:25.366
He's always vaguely creepy
during my exams

16:25.368 --> 16:28.302
but not in a direct way
that I can really call him on.

16:28.304 --> 16:29.220
[LAUGHS]

16:29.222 --> 16:32.190
Oh, Dr. Fist, what a hound.

16:32.192 --> 16:34.576
[♪]

16:35.877 --> 16:38.546
[YAWNS]

16:38.548 --> 16:40.281
Kids, wake up.

16:40.283 --> 16:42.984
Right now, so I can fix
your breakfast.

16:42.986 --> 16:45.887
All right, beautiful boy,
here's your bacon

16:45.889 --> 16:47.922
and fresh-baked croissants.

16:47.924 --> 16:51.225
<i>Merci,</i> Papa.

16:51.227 --> 16:53.727
And your coffee.
Black as Atlanta.

16:53.729 --> 16:55.163
Thank you.

16:55.165 --> 16:56.830
You're not still mad at me?

16:56.832 --> 16:59.083
Mad at you? I should thank you.

16:59.085 --> 17:01.619
Being a homemaker
is the toughest job

17:01.621 --> 17:02.854
I've ever loved.

17:02.856 --> 17:07.525
With the best benefits
and the shortest commute.

17:07.527 --> 17:09.410
[♪]

17:12.431 --> 17:16.067
Cleveland,
can I ask you for some advice?

17:16.069 --> 17:18.719
What's the problem?
Talk to me about it.

17:18.721 --> 17:22.473
Donna, she needs honest advice
and cranberry juice.

17:22.475 --> 17:25.042
Oh, well, let me get
it for you, Roberta.

17:25.044 --> 17:26.060
[GROWLS]

17:26.062 --> 17:27.394
Ow, my face.

17:27.396 --> 17:30.031
Donna.
Oh, my God. My baby.

17:30.033 --> 17:32.433
You do not hit a child.

17:32.435 --> 17:34.451
It was instinctive.
I didn't mean to.

17:34.453 --> 17:38.506
Enough. For shame,
Donna. For shame.

17:38.508 --> 17:41.842
And you, no scare. No.

17:41.844 --> 17:44.012
Yes, sir, Cleveland.

17:44.014 --> 17:46.180
All I needed was some parenting.

17:46.182 --> 17:48.316
Shame.

17:51.086 --> 17:53.387
[♪]

17:53.389 --> 17:56.024
So Cleveland's
the homemaker now.

17:56.026 --> 17:59.260
And the truth is, he's better
at it than I ever was.

17:59.262 --> 18:02.696
[SIGHS]
To be honest, I don't even know
what my role is.

18:02.698 --> 18:04.966
Well, Donna,
it's a nice of change of pace

18:04.968 --> 18:07.335
to have a drink
with a sad, whining woman

18:07.337 --> 18:09.837
but, uh, you know,
I-I'm sick of seeing you

18:09.839 --> 18:11.306
all down in your mouth.

18:11.308 --> 18:13.507
I mean-- I mean, who are you?
Answer me.

18:13.509 --> 18:16.778
Well, I'm-- I'm Donna.

18:16.780 --> 18:19.147
No, you are a lioness.

18:19.149 --> 18:22.283
And no one is going to displace
you or you will roar.

18:22.285 --> 18:23.284
Now, who are you?

18:23.286 --> 18:25.703
I am a lioness.
ALL: Yeah.

18:25.705 --> 18:27.638
It's my house.
ALL: Yeah.

18:27.640 --> 18:29.140
And you know what?

18:29.142 --> 18:31.025
I'm going to the Crutched
by an Angel dinner

18:31.027 --> 18:33.561
to let Cleveland know
that that's my charity.

18:33.563 --> 18:35.163
I run the show.

18:36.414 --> 18:37.715
Yeah.
You go, Donna.

18:37.717 --> 18:40.418
Charity is what defines you.

18:40.420 --> 18:41.619
Yeah.
Yeah.

18:41.621 --> 18:43.388
Yeah.
That's right.

18:43.390 --> 18:46.024
My roommate and I
are having a showering contest.

18:46.026 --> 18:48.592
Will you guys be the judges?
Get out of here.

18:48.594 --> 18:51.095
Yeah, we're watching
<i>The Cleveland Show.</i>

18:51.097 --> 18:53.030
[CLASSICAL MUSIC PLAYING]

18:53.032 --> 18:54.364
Hello, everyone.

18:54.366 --> 18:56.166
Please, either take your seat

18:56.168 --> 18:59.704
or remain seated
forever as applicable.

18:59.706 --> 19:02.106
I'd like to introduce
the newest member

19:02.108 --> 19:05.710
of the CBAA family,
Cleveland Brown.

19:05.712 --> 19:08.545
[AUDIENCE APPLAUDING]

19:08.547 --> 19:09.880
Wow.

19:09.882 --> 19:12.182
This is--

19:12.184 --> 19:14.151
Wow.

19:14.153 --> 19:19.223
To all of you plegics,
both para- and quadra-

19:19.225 --> 19:22.559
I may be able to run a mile
and bathe myself

19:22.561 --> 19:25.129
and compete
on <i>Dancing With the Stars</i>

19:25.131 --> 19:27.598
should my prayers be answered.

19:27.600 --> 19:29.900
Please, Xenu.

19:29.902 --> 19:32.420
However--
Hold up.

19:32.422 --> 19:34.405
Donna, what are you doing here?

19:34.407 --> 19:37.108
You've never been
interested in charity.

19:37.110 --> 19:39.410
That is not--

19:39.412 --> 19:41.879
Cleveland, I have something
to share

19:41.881 --> 19:43.114
with you and everyone here

19:43.116 --> 19:45.383
especially the women.

19:45.385 --> 19:47.001
I had it all.

19:47.003 --> 19:50.438
I was a mother, a wife
and a career woman.

19:50.440 --> 19:52.306
Yes, it was a lot of work.

19:52.308 --> 19:54.742
But it's woman's work.

19:54.744 --> 19:56.126
This woman.

19:56.128 --> 19:58.730
And I am taking back my home.

19:58.732 --> 20:01.231
No. Nothing has ever made me

20:01.233 --> 20:04.868
feel so worthy,
so indispensable.

20:04.870 --> 20:08.239
Please, Cleveland.
Let me do what I was born to do.

20:08.241 --> 20:09.674
Everything.

20:09.676 --> 20:12.744
All right.

20:12.746 --> 20:13.978
Because I love you.

20:13.980 --> 20:16.881
I love you too, Cleveland.

20:16.883 --> 20:18.549
AUDIENCE:
Ah.

20:21.085 --> 20:22.753
What's going on? I can't see.

20:22.755 --> 20:25.222
Thanks for putting me
in the back.

20:28.910 --> 20:29.994
[LAUGHING]

20:29.996 --> 20:31.295
She bought it.

20:31.297 --> 20:33.114
[LAUGHING]

20:33.116 --> 20:34.815
I wish you could've been here

20:34.817 --> 20:38.052
when I gave that stupid lioness
speech that you wrote.

20:38.054 --> 20:40.054
I'm the one who
was willing to kill her

20:40.056 --> 20:41.355
to see if she was faking it.

20:41.357 --> 20:43.523
And I played
the redneck hayseed.

20:43.525 --> 20:47.461
Here's to dum-dum,
the love of my life.

20:47.463 --> 20:51.231
I'll teach him to wash
my dishes in my house.

20:51.233 --> 20:53.534
Wait. What the fuck
am I doing?

20:55.671 --> 20:57.638
[♪]

21:28.770 --> 21:31.706
[English - US - Line 21]
